						<summary>

						<p>Stone standing in Huraḷimakki field.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record refers to <hi rend="italic">mahāpradhāna</hi> Achyutasēnabōva and to the village Banahāḍi and mentions the royal palace at <hi rend="bold">Bārahakanyāpura.</hi></p>						

						<p>It is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1112, Sādhāraṇa, Vṛiśchika 12, Thursday</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1190 A.D., November 8.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
